INSERT INTO `character_add_info` VALUES (1,1,'cg','<p>Father: James de\'Blanc, Mother: Annemarie de\'Blanc, Brother: Royce de\'Blanc</p>','','','','','','<p>Rory is&nbsp;fiesty, determined, and very loyal to her friends.</p>',4),(2,5,'cg','<p>Father: James de\'Blanc, Mother: Annemarie de\'Blanc, Sister: Rory de\'Blanc</p>','<p>The de\'Blanc family was ousted from the throne when Royce was five years old. His father began smuggling, and he was practically raised on the smuggling vessel&nbsp;<em>The Annemarie</em>. Royce has heard about his family\'s rightful claim on the throne growing up and, even though the rest of the family has moved on, is determined to reclaim the throne from the de\'Liraans.</p>','','','<p>The de\'Blanc family</p>','','<p>Royce is fiery and stubborn, unwilling to give up until he has achieved his goals.</p>',4),(3,7,'','<p>Father: Cornelius de\'Halle, Mother: Christabell de\'Halle, Brother: Denny de\'Halle, Sisters: Kati, Mac, and Tal de\'Halle</p>','<p>Neither of Tanner\'s parents were that interested in him and his siblings, leaving him to raise his four younger siblings. When he was 14, their mother ran off with another man. Not interested in staying with their disinterested, alcoholic father, Tanner took his siblings and left home. They\'ve been on their own for the last three years, doing their best to stay together. Prior to ending up with the rebels, Tanner would work odd jobs and steal to provide for them. They have not had any contact with either parent since they left home.</p>','','','','','',4),(4,13,'cg','<p>Father: Edward Emerson (deceased), Mother: Eva Emerson, Sister: Adeline Emerson</p>','','<ul>\r\n<li>Science</li>\r\n<li>Lime green</li>\r\n<li>Having superpowers</li>\r\n<li>Cherry slushies</li>\r\n</ul>','<ul>\r\n<li>Mad scientists</li>\r\n</ul>','','<p>Tyler Avery</p>','',18),(5,27,'cg','<p>Brother: Kasen, Sister: Melyntha (deceased), Brother-in-law: Joyn Sedrec, Uncle: Carrick</p>','<p>Emeric and his siblings were mostly kept hidden from the world, especially after his paranoid mother was killed causing his father to be fearful for the children\'s safety. When Emeric was 16, his father died and he became king of Risteara. He was a weak, unpopular king and took bad advice from a questionable advisor, even turning on his loyal twin brother Kasen. He was deposed by a nobleman named Zavion and exiled to the neighboring country of Bruntain where his mother\'s brother King Carrick ruled.</p>','','','<p>King Zavion, Joyn Sedrec</p>','<p>Kasen, Nolan Aishley, Cal Remick</p>','<p>Outgoing and charming, Emeric can usual win anyone\'s confidence. Having learned from his mistakes, he has lost much of his arrogance and is trying to improve. However, he can still be quite manipulative.</p>',28),(6,25,'lg','<p>Brother: Kasen, Sister: Melyntha (deceased), Brother-in-law: Joyn Sedrec, Uncle: Carrick</p>','<p>He grew up with his brother Emeric and his sister Melyntha, mostly hidden from the rest of the kingdom due to their parents\' paranoia. His father and sister died when he was 16 and, following the advice of a questionable advisor, his brother accused him and his brother-in-law Joyn Sedrec of plotting against him to take the throne. His brother&nbsp;was deposed by a nobleman named Zavion, and Kasen left the country to live in Bruntain with his maternal uncle King Carrick, who gave him lands in Bruntain. He did not speak to his brother for about a year, but eventually Emeric apologized and they made peace, going into business together. They now co-own a large merchant fleet.</p>','','','<p>King Zavion</p>','<p>Emeric, Nolan, Joyn Sedrec</p>','<p>Kasen is quiet and a bit reserved, preferring to stay on the edge of things.</p>',28),(7,26,'cn','<p>Mother: Devara (deceased), Adopted Father: Gilboth Zando</p>','<p>Cal grew up in her mother\'s circus. After her mother\'s death and the circus disolved, she was adopted by Gilboth Zando, a con man turned circus magician who she often helped with tricks. He returned to the life of crime, teaching her his skills. They determine a target, usually a wealthy house; Gilboth becomes friends with the target, casing the location and distracting the owner; and then Cal breaks in and robs the place. Their scheme has worked well, but they have both been arrested after their latest job went wrong.</p>','','','<p>King Zavion, Nolan Aishley</p>','<p>Prince Thierry, Emeric</p>','',28),(8,30,'cg','<p>Father: Nat X (deceased), Mother: Luna X (deceased), Brothers: Sterling X (deceased), Jett X (deceased), Matt X (deceased), Toby X, Sisters-in-law: Ava X, Nina X (deceased), Nephew: Zane X, Niece: Aria Mathis</p>','','','','<p>Jett X, Miles Stanley</p>','<p>Toby X, Alex Sky, Tom Pearson</p>','<p>Elisa is very loyal and always speaks her mind.</p>',28),(9,29,'','<p>Father: Nat X (deceased), Mother: Luna X (deceased), Brothers: Sterling X (deceased), Jett X (deceased), Matt X (deceased), Toby X, Sisters-in-law: Ava X, Nina X (deceased), Nephew: Zane X, Niece: Aria Mathis</p>','','','','<p>The X Family, other than Elisa</p>','<p>Leanna, Elisa X</p>','<p>Mild mannered and a bit hapless, Toby is often underestimated.</p>',28),(10,28,'','<p>Father: Finlay Wallace, Mother: Elizabeth Monty, Step-Father: Francis Monty, Half-Brothers: Percival Monty, Richard Monty (deceased), Half-Sisters: Margaret Monty, Abigail Monty</p>','','','','','','',28),(11,12,'lg','<p>Father: Owen Blair (deceased), Mother: Danica Jackson Blair (deceased), Uncles: Daniel Blair, David Jackson</p>','','','','<p>Jeffrey Anderson, Ezekiel Schroeder</p>','<p>Aidan Anderson, Ellie Duncan</p>','<p>Rochell is quiet and a little on the shy side, but is stronger than people guess and is dedicated to doing what is right.</p>',18),(12,15,'cg','<p>Father: Seth Avery, Mother: Sarah Avery (deceased), Brother: Tyler Avery, Uncles: Ezekiel Schroeder, Zach S.</p>','<p>Olivia\'s parents and her uncle Ezekiel Schroeder worked on a super serum together, but, while they perfected it, her mother did not want her or her brother Tyler to take it. That was fine with Olivia, but Tyler wanted it and, after the mysterious deaths of their parents, took the serum. When Olivia realized that her uncle was behind her parents\' deaths, she tried to convince Tyler to leave with her, but he refused. She has enrolled in a spy training program to gain the skills she needs to rescue her brother from their uncle.</p>','','','<p>Ezekiel Schroeder</p>','<p>Andi Anderson, Ellie Duncan, Rochelle Blair, Aidan Anderson</p>','<p>Olivia is determined to reach her goals, no matter the cost.</p>',18),(13,41,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(14,42,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(15,40,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(17,2,'lg','<p>Father: Dedrec de\'Liraan (deceased), Mother: Shandra de\'Liraan,&nbsp;Brother: Cael de\'Liraan,&nbsp;Nephew: Ian de\'Liraan,&nbsp;Uncle: Josef de\'Liraan,&nbsp;Cousin: Ronius de\'Liraan</p>','','','','','','',4),(19,9,'','<p>Father: Allen O\'Conner, Mother: Jocelyn McGuire, Brother: Kaleb O\'Conner, Sister: Kaley O\'Conner</p>','','','','<p>Shade Ryder, Drake, Shannon</p>','<p>Devin, Trevor, Hunter, Beck, Fido, Isabella</p>','<p>Katia is outgoing and friendly and is a terrible liar.</p>',4),(20,11,'lg','<p>Father: Jeremy Anderson, Mother: Cassie Anderson, Uncles: Jeffrey Anderson, Matthew Anderson, Aunts: Elizabeth Anderson Jackson, Helen Anderson, Cousins: Andi Anderson, Ellie Duncan, Tony Duncan</p>','','<ul>\r\n<li>Superheroes</li>\r\n<li>Flying</li>\r\n<li>Ice cream</li>\r\n</ul>','','<p>Jeffrey Anderson, Ezekiel Schroeder</p>','<p>Ellie Duncan, Rochelle Blair, Cody Parker, Andi Anderson, Tony Duncan</p>','',18),(21,14,'','<p>Father: Seth Avery, Mother: Sarah Avery (deceased), Sister: Olivia Avery, Uncles: Ezekiel Schroeder, Zach S.</p>','','','','<p>Ezekiel Schroeder</p>','<p>Kelsey Emerson, Ellie Duncan, Dominique Stafford</p>','',18),(22,10,'cg','<p>Father: Mack Reynolds (deceased), Mother: Elizabeth Anderson Jackson, Step-Father: David Jackson, Brother: Tony Duncan</p>','','','','<p>Jeffrey Anderson, Ezekiel Schroeder</p>','<p>Aidan Anderson, Rochelle Blair, Tyler Avery</p>','<p>Ellie is fiery and independent. She speaks her mind and is determined to achieve her goals, even if she has to use unorthodox means to get there.</p>',18),(23,20,'','','','','','<p>Theo Fitzroy, Carl Ellery</p>','<p>Brendan Frost</p>','<p>Alek\'s charming, friendly demeanor hides his fears.</p>',18),(24,17,'ng','<p>First husband: Mack Reynolds (deceased), Second husband: David Jackson, Children: Tony Duncan, Ellie Duncan, Brothers: Jeffrey Anderson, Jeremy Anderson, Matthew Anderson, Nieces: Andi Anderson, Rochelle Blair, Nephew: Aidan Anderson</p>','<p>She discovered her superpowers in her teens, along with her older brother Jeffrey and twin brother Jeremy. Jeffrey turned evil, and Elizabeth ran away with and married Jeffrey\'s former sidekick Mac Reynolds. Having no idea about&nbsp;the marriage or that they had had children, Jeffrey tracked down Mac and murdered him, along with another superpowered rival Danica Jackson. Elizabeth changed her name and went into hiding with the two children. Eventually, when trying to help her twin escape from their older brother, Jeffrey kidnapped Elizabeth, leading both of her children to Shadow Rock City (where she had last been seen) and to the other superheroes.</p>','','','<p>Jeffrey Anderson, Ezekiel Schroeder</p>','','',18);
